(2660, 'en', 'default', '6e133f59352723c84d8036ce4b20ad51', 'We added measures on the post type and taxonomy slug inputs to prevent using characters that should not be used in slugs. This is primarily for when adding new post types and taxonomies, but will also affect when editing existing options. Do not hesitate to contact support if you are experiencing issues.', NULL, 'LINE', NULL, 0, '', '79c73f23f7f0f9823839f6c6407d6a7d'),
