(510, 26, 'jobs_morphean_0_content_job_morphean', '<strong>Your mission:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>To support management and the marketing and sales team in the areas of administration, organisation and contracts.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Your main tasks:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Organise and coordinate management’s operational activities</li>\r\n 	<li>Monitor and manage partner relations</li>\r\n 	<li>Follow up with contracts and other administrative details</li>\r\n 	<li>Organise and coordinate meetings and events</li>\r\n 	<li>Organise and prepare board meetings</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Ideal profile:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Business CFC</li>\r\n 	<li>Diploma as a Director’s assistant or solid experience as an assistant</li>\r\n 	<li>Experience (3-5 years) in the administration of an SME</li>\r\n 	<li>Native German or French speaker with fluency in English, or English mother tongue with fluency in German and/or French.</li>\r\n 	<li>Customer-oriented self-starter</li>\r\n 	<li>Excellent communicator</li>\r\n 	<li>C permit or Swiss nationality, Swiss resident</li>\r\n 	<li>Location: Fribourg (Granges-Paccot)</li>\r\n 	<li>Age: 25-45</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>We offer you:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>A dynamic environment where you can work autonomously</li>\r\n 	<li>Possibility to work part time</li>\r\n 	<li>A young and innovative atmosphere</li>\r\n 	<li>Opportunities for professional development within the company</li>\r\n 	<li>Experience in different business sectors (security, retail, healthcare, etc.)</li>\r\n 	<li>A corporate structure dedicated to encouraging innovation</li>\r\n 	<li>A plan for continuing education with numerous training opportunities</li>\r\n</ul>'),
