(518, 134, 'jobs_morphean_0_content_job_morphean', '<div id="ui-accordion-1-panel-0" class="accordion_content no_icon ui-accordion-content ui-helper-reset ui-widget-content ui-corner-bottom ui-accordion-content-active">\r\n<div class="accordion_content_inner">\r\n<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element ">\r\n<div class="wpb_wrapper">\r\n\r\n<strong>Your mission:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Centralise and support the requests from the Morphean international sales team in order to validate the technical needs of the customers. Support the sales team remotely and on site in Europe.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Your main tasks:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Manage and answer customers’ specifications to validate the technical part</li>\r\n 	<li>Train the customers and partners on the usage of our products</li>\r\n 	<li>Support the partners during their first installation</li>\r\n 	<li>Train and support the sales team in order to improve their products’ knowledge</li>\r\n 	<li>Assist the salesman on the answer of tenders</li>\r\n 	<li>Assist the salesman on site (mainly European countries)</li>\r\n 	<li>Consolidate and detail the customers’ demands in order to forward qualified information to the product manager</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Your background:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Bachelor of Science / MSE Master of Science in Computer Science, Telecommunication, or Engineering or similar studies</li>\r\n 	<li>or a solid experience in IP video surveillance with good IT skills</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Your professional experiences:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>A minimum of 3 years experiences in software or IT / Telecom domain</li>\r\n 	<li>Experience in IP video surveillance may be an advantage</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Our expectations:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Confident with computers and the relevant applications (Web, CRM, Microsoft Office)</li>\r\n 	<li>Native speaking German or Italian or French with good confidence in one other language. English is a “Must”.</li>\r\n 	<li>Customer oriented personality with initiative spirits, confident to work independently</li>\r\n 	<li>Good communication skills</li>\r\n 	<li>Swiss or C permit holder, living in Switzerland</li>\r\n 	<li>Work’s location: Fribourg (Granges-Paccot) with journey in Europe</li>\r\n 	<li>Age: 25 – 45 years old</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>What we offer:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Participate in the success of an innovative company aiming to become the leader on the market!</li>\r\n 	<li>Work within a dynamic, young and innovative team</li>\r\n 	<li>The chance to work in an autonomous way</li>\r\n 	<li>Opportunity for professional development within the company</li>\r\n 	<li>Experiences in many different market segments (security, retail, healthcare, industry, etc.)</li>\r\n 	<li>Compensation and working package that meets a high level in the industry</li>\r\n 	<li>A training plan with a variety of possibilities which will improve your skills and experiences</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>'),
