(538, 136, 'sous-titre_page', '<h3>Morphean – Swiss / Smart / Secure!</h3>\r\nMorphean is the only VSaaS dedicated company! Morphean offers a totally new way to get the best from the video surveillance cameras. Morphean is a Swiss company, located in Fribourg who was founded in 2009 as a spin-off from Softcom Technologies (2001).\r\n\r\nMorphean’s mission is to bring to the market innovative video surveillance solutions, especially hosted video management platforms, incident detection and video content analysis technology. In order to re-enforce our team and to support the international launch of our products in Europe we are seeking for :'),
